    "body" : "<p>The easiest way would probably be to convert the array into a java.util.ArrayList.  Once it is in an arraylist, you can easily leverage the contains method.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static boolean bagOfWords(String str)\n{\n    String[] words = {\"word1\", \"word2\", \"word3\", \"word4\", \"word5\"};  \n    return (Arrays.asList(words).contains(str));\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
