    "body" : "<p>You can use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#matches%28java.lang.String%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">String#matches</a> method like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.printf(\"Matches - [%s]%n\", string.matches(\"^.*?(item1|item2|item3).*$\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
