    "body" : "<p>And if you are looking for case insensitive match, use pattern</p>\n<pre><code>Pattern pattern = Pattern.compile(&quot;\\\\bitem1 |item2\\\\b&quot;,java.util.regex.Pattern.CASE_INSENSITIVE);\n\nMatcher matcher = pattern.matcher(input);\nif (matcher.find()) { \n    ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
